text: Bahati is an estate in Nairobi, the capital of Kenya. Administratively, it is a location in Pumwani division of NairobiUN Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA): Kenya_AdminLevels_1-4 and Kamukunji Constituency. In 2005 the Bahati location had an estimated population of 55,082. == References == Category:Suburbs of Nairobi
title: Bahati, Nairobi
